OL,3,CWater firm faces criminal charges over
OL,4,Cblast that killed four
OL,6,FWessex Water will face criminal
OL,7,Fcharges in connection with a fatal
OL,8,Fexplosion that killed four workers,
OL,9,Fincluding a 16-year-old apprentice.
OL,11,FLuke Wheaton, 16, Ray White, 57, Brian
OL,12,FVickery, 63, and Mike James, 64, died
OL,13,Fin the blast at the company's water
OL,14,Ftreatment site in Avonmouth, in
OL,15,FBristol, in December 2020.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
