OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1784231286
OL,3,CWater firm faces criminal charges over
OL,4,Cblast that killed four
OL,6,FAvon and Somerset Police dropped its
OL,7,Finvestigation into the explosion in
OL,8,FJuly 2024 because the evidence did not
OL,9,Freach "the extremely high threshold to
OL,10,Fprosecute any criminal offence of
OL,11,Fmanslaughter."
OL,13,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,14,Fhas now informed Wessex Water of its
OL,15,Fintention to prosecute.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
