OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1784231286
OL,3,CWater firm faces criminal charges over
OL,4,Cblast that killed four
OL,6,FA HSE spokesperson said: "Following an
OL,7,Finvestigation by the Health and Safety
OL,8,FExecutive into an incident at
OL,9,FAvonmouth on 3 December 2020, which
OL,10,Fresulted in the deaths of four
OL,11,Fworkers, our Legal Services Division
OL,12,Fhas taken the decision to authorise
OL,13,Fcriminal charges against Wessex Water,
OL,14,Ffor offences under the Health and
OL,15,FSafety at Work Act."
OL,17,FThe explosion took place in a silo
OL,18,Fcontaining biosolids - a product of
OL,19,Fwastewater treatment processes which
OL,20,Fcan be used as fertiliser.
OL,26,@wD@TO]
