OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1784231286
OL,3,CWater firm faces criminal charges over
OL,4,Cblast that killed four
OL,6,FThe workers were on the roof of the
OL,7,Fsilo when a spark ignited.
OL,9,FMr White and Mr Vickery were employees
OL,10,Fof Wessex Water, while Mr James was a
OL,11,Fcontractor working at the site.
OL,13,F16-year-old Mr Wheaton was working as
OL,14,Fan apprentice at the firm.
OL,16,FMr Wheaton's family previously said
OL,17,Fthat he was "the most gorgeous,
OL,18,Floving, happy, talented, perfect son."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
